Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Ex-GDR Interior Minister: Dozens of </F>
Stasi Spies in Austria"] 
  [Text] In an exclusive interview for KURIER, Peter-Michael 
Diestel, former GDR interior minister and Christian Democratic 
Union [CDU] Landtag deputy in Brandenburg, has confirmed that 
several Austrians were employed by the Stasi and that they are 
quite possibly continuing their work for other intelligence 
services. 

